name: Wondering Raine 925 Stirling Silver Earrings
description:
This necklace is part of a collection I call Wondering Raine.

Raine is a painting (oil on canvas) that I call Wondering Raine. The painting inspired me create a design I call a wearable canvas.

Wondering Rainie 925 Stirling Silver Earrings . Raine is handcrafted with polymer clay molded and fired by me with a purple glass bead to represent the sky in the painting. 

I took utter care crafting this piece and feel like my painting its small piece of art.

Health and happiness to you.

Vx
